{"tid":344310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警隊醜聞】涉事警長要紀律調查   性感女係內地女遊客","createTime":"2017-08-02T07:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T08:22:57.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3926bfbc3dde3cb63ea7a26a137462ef10d51dda","tid":344310,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170802/large/1501656381_f86c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170802%2Flarge%2F1501656381_f86c.jpg&h=6504e69d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴警署發生警務人員涉偷拍女報案人事件(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2uSOixH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2uSOixH&d=XxgMDdj0BcTCoetgCbYGdxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=75e3bfa5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2uSOixH</a>)，據悉涉事警長當日駐守報案室任助理值日官，他現時正接受內部紀律調查。一般而言，警方會調查涉事警務人員有否違反內部指引，可能會發出書面警告，料對其仕途有所影響。<br />\n<br />\n而事件中的女報案人，為內地女遊客，據了解，她發現其信用卡簽賬有問題，遂到警署查詢有關事宜，但警方僅能提供意見，並著她到銀行查詢相關事宜，但為她記下報案紀錄。尖沙嘴警署迄今未有收到女事主投訴遭偷拍事宜。"},{"pid":"3a963247871fab4388704756f0ec4c3c3ef80278","tid":344310,"uid":26752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T08:00:15.000Z","msg":"阿sir做野唔先你教"},{"pid":"e2992f53b3ccfe66824e02b31ffa4b5f71e3ec8c","tid":344310,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T08:00:16.000Z","msg":"支那雞  <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無比黑警拉入認人室強姦算佢好彩啦！"},{"pid":"bf999e0cb37064ab7b9c17bbd4e81d24f9b57a91","tid":344310,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T08:00:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿sir做野唔先你教</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n阿sir影大波波唔洗你教"},{"pid":"9e66b7df1480848620049fc56387c2be9da605c7","tid":344310,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T08:01:45.000Z","msg":"黑警 -&gt; (進化)  黑獸警"},{"pid":"69171e5e40021f450dcb01b00